# first meeting
chat trigger "NotZ says: I run a blacksmith shop here and craft pickaxes."
chat trigger "NotZ says: My brother in the house to the east crafts the best armors."
chat trigger "NotZ says: You need to supply me the ingots. I need 5 ingots and a pickaxe template. I'll craft any pickaxe for you, 3k gp a piece."
addCondition trigger blacksmithnotz
